{
  "stem": "13457.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the things-- things were quite bad and everybody was sick, then I, being more resilient to the extent that I was 11 years old, I used to go on the market and-- and I sort of tried to get the best deal out of every watermelon or every bunch of grapes that I would buy from these Hosbach peasants.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, just short of all of us, actually, going bye-bye, so to speak, to the other world, the transport came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they brought us to the-- to the-- to the-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] --a port on the Caspian Sea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went on a ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, it was a long climb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We're in-- in-- in desert conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no water there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember my mother gave her watch to somebody for a glass of water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was, again, the Jews were not taken by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there was one guy sneaking by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he says, let me carry your-- your luggage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I will-- can sneak on the ship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "On the ship, everybody had diarrheas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But the point is, that by that time, I already had my shakes of malaria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was shaking just about everyday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And by the time we landed in Pahlavi, which was already, so to speak, resurrection, it was a little beach in Persia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And for the first time, I went to the fence and some Persian sold us eggs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I think, it was the first egg I have seen, maybe, in two years or so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we, between the three of us, we had 18 eggs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And malaria was shaking me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But then we got medicine for-- for malaria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my father was still very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
